## üöÄ Features

### Core Functionality
- **üîí Automatic System Locking**: Intelligent proximity-based system security
- **üì± Bluetooth Device Detection**: Real-time monitoring of paired mobile devices
- **‚ö° Cross-Platform Compatibility**: Native support for Windows, macOS, and Linux
- **üéØ Configurable Sensitivity**: Adjustable detection parameters for optimal performance

### Advanced Features
- **üîÑ Background Monitoring**: Daemon-thread based monitoring with minimal resource usage
- **üõ°Ô∏è Safety Thresholds**: Multi-layered detection to prevent false positives
- **üìä Real-time Status**: Live monitoring dashboard with detailed system state
- **üíæ Persistent Configuration**: JSON-based configuration with automatic backup
- **üé® Interactive CLI**: Color-coded terminal interface with intuitive commands

### Technical Specifications
- **Bluetooth Stack**: PyBluez integration for robust device discovery
- **Threading Model**: Asynchronous monitoring with proper synchronization
- **Configuration Management**: Hierarchical configuration with environment overrides
- **Error Handling**: Comprehensive exception management with graceful degradation

